rComments: I had Joe as a Calculus TA at Scarborough campus. He spends a lot of time taking care of individual students' questions and exploring problems. He does a great job of giving people the tools to solve problems -- those that are interested. The students who ignored him and sat in the back of the room were ignored in turn. Very good TA.
